description:
Get tickets to the games, concerts, and theater shows you want to see – or sell them when you can’t go – right from the StubHub app. Our FanProtect™ Guarantee means we back every order, so you can buy and sell tickets with 100% confidence. Plus, with All-in Pricing, the price you see on StubHub is the price you pay. Every ticket. Every day.

FEATURES

• 4,000+ interactive maps: Filter ticket listings by section and see the view from your section before you buy on select venue maps
• Price alerts: Tell us what you want to pay and get notifications when there's a match
• Mobile tickets: Get into select events with mobile tickets on your iPhone – no need to print!* 
• Passbook: Add your tickets to Passbook and scan your iPhone to get into your event*
• Local info: Find bars, restaurants, and parking near the venue
• Barcode scanning: Scan ticket barcodes when you list to attract more buyers and keep your tickets listed longer*
• My Account: Check your orders, manage your listings, see your payout, and more

* Available for select teams and venues
